{"tid":1682794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"URGENT 緊急！ 今晚8:00，元天助屯！","createTime":"2019-10-30T09:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:19:12.000Z","uid":296535,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c6cf985c3dfa2ba92453ca98c105144f060bf7e","tid":1682794,"uid":296535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>！⬇️天水圍人請進:<br />\n[突發] 天水圍人今晚八點銀座！！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1682636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1682636</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">！⬇️元朗人！看！</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗人，今晚不論如何，一定要幫屯門牛引狗！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都係嗰句,7-8 yoho<br />\n8點打後，老地方！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f1b6a98196a3f191fef9e9164c50c13a9d203ae1","tid":1682794,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:26:02.000Z","msg":"其實要達成目標<br />\n不外乎都係開源節流<br />\n開源，好簡單，姐係要令對方加入己方陣營<br />\n都係教育佢地民主是個好東西<br />\n<br />\n但有d 長者唔會明<br />\n咁呢個時候就要節流<br />\n佢地班口撐支那唔緊要<br />\n肉體懼怕支那先最實際<br />\n正如有d 人口裡反美心，身體卻去食元氣<br />\n呢d 真係唔太實際囉<br />\n<br />\n為左節流<br />\n大家快d share 文宣比長者睇<br />\n支那嘅恐怖真係隨時影響到香港<br />\n到時棺材都無埋就好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3ADQhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3ADQhD.jpg&h=fbfa3f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L003CF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F